title: Jack Dorsey
deleted: All the supposed Philantropy in the world cannot wash away the fact that Dorsey changed the Twitter rules for Trump so he can continue spreadg his violent and racist messages.

title: Jack Dorsey
added: However, despite the ban of his account, President Donald Trump was easily able to open alternative accounts, garnering hundreds of thousands of followers within mere hours; those followers fully aware of his account ban.
Not such an effective strategy apparently.

The permanence of Trump's Twitter account ban was viewed by many as not only an extremely petty move against a political opponent and idealogy Dorsey desperately despised, yet felt powerless to control, it was also just as clearly the continuation of a petty "social media mogul pissing contest", as Facebook a day earlier reported it would be blocking Donald Trump's account until inauguration day, just a day after announcing that there would be a 24 hour ban of Donald Trump's account, in response to Twitter first banning Trump's account access for 8 hours.
